                <div class="total">24 Points</div>
                <p style="font-size: 8.5pt; margin-bottom: 8px;">Three-engine convergence: Technical structure, fundamental thesis, and microstructure/positioning dynamics. Requires alignment across all three dimensions.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 7.5pt; color: #666;"><em>Minimum to enter: 20/24 for Tier 1</em></p>
