                <p style="font-size: 7.5pt; color: #666;"><em>Minimum to enter: 8/12</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Key Insight -->
        <div class="insight-box">
            <strong>Key Insight:</strong> The books are entry frameworks, not holding period constraints. Entry logic determines how you get in. Price and drivers determine how long you stay. A Technical Overlay position that catches a fundamental tailwind can graduate to Core Book treatment.
        </div>

        <!-- Graduation -->
        <div class="graduation">
            <h4>POSITION GRADUATION</h4>
            <p>Positions can move between books as drivers evolve:</p>
            <div class="flow-boxes">
